name: The Jordan Family
description: This was a wonderful mountain top setting, full of robust family portraits with the fog and Rocky Mountains in the backdrop. Full of close up shots, landscape, and more.

name: Practically Pawfect
description: This project was done to show off some amazing puppies and their naturally photogenic and energized personalities.

name: Brave and Daring
description: Brave and daring takes risks with different camera angles and styles of shooting to look at the risk and reward types of photos that are produced.

name: Football Family
description: This describes how much fun a family cookout can be with just you, your wife, and kids. The natural ombiance that a wood fired grill, some burgers, and a autumn night sky can create while gearing up to watch some football.

name: Crazy Compliation
description: This set depics the randomness and craze that a family can have while trying to take photos, the natural emotions in each of the photos gives off a genuine felling like no prepared pose for a camera can capture
